	(36,'Potter S Homogenizer','<p>Homogeniser Potter S is well-established and suited for gentle  disruption of soft tissues or cultured cells. Shearing forces that  originate during the passage of samples between cylinder wall and  plunger provide well-controlled conditions that even allow the isolation  of intact nuclei from such materials. An integrated cooling vessel,  filled with ice water or connected to an external cooling system, helps  to control heating of the sample during homogenisation in order to slow  down degradation processes. Cylinders are safely held in place by a  clamping system in the top of the cooling vessel, thereby protecting the  user from glass breakage. A large selection of cylinders and plungers  ia available.</p>','<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"293\" height=\"53\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line voltage</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>230 V</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line frequency</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>50 Hertz</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Wattage</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>70 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"493\" height=\"187\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>300 x 300 x 850 mm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weight</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>12,5 kg</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection type</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>IP20</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Connections</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Class I cold socket, separate cable approx. 3 m</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection class</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>I</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interference</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Class B according to EN 55014</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Setting|display</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Analog</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Max. ambie