	(42,'Certomat BS-1','<div class=\"csc-default\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<h3>Description</h3>\r\n<p>Incubation shaker CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> BS-1 is suited for the  growth of bacteria, yeast, insect and plant cells in a  temperature-controlled environment from 8 &deg;C above ambient temperature  up to 70 &deg;C. With an optional integrated cooling unit, the temperature  range can be extended to 10 &deg;C below ambient temperature. Also available  is an optional illumination unit for growth of photosynthetic  organisms. CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> BS-1 can be programmed to operate for  specified periods at defined ranges of speed and temperature plus  illumination. Five programs, each consisting of four steps and one  pre-step, can be defined and stored. The menue language can be selected  by the user. CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> BS-1 units can be stacked three units  high in order to save valuable lab space. Due to the patented adjustable  mass compensation system, all three stacked units can be run at maximum  speed even when fully loaded.</p>\r\n<h3>Obligatory Shaker Accessories</h3>\r\n<p>To make it functional,  every CERTOMAT&reg; shaker or incubation shaker requires a tray. Available  tray sizes are 420 x 420 mm (E/EU) and 800 x 420 mm (F/FU). Suitable  trays, clamps and further accessories are listed with each instrument.</p>\r\n</div>','<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"436\" height=\"120\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interior dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>89 x 65 x 49,5 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Orbital shaking amplitude</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>25 mm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stacking</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Up to 3 units without speed reduction</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>650 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cooling capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr