	(45,'Certomat T-Plus','<div class=\"csc-default\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<h3>Description</h3>\r\n<p>Incubation shaker CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> Tplus is suited for the  growth of bacteria, yeast, insect and plant cells in a  temperature-controlled environment from 10&deg; C below ambient temperature  up to 70&deg; C. Also available is an optional illumination unit for growth  of photosynthetic organisms. CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> Tplus is programmed  via touch screen to operate at defined speed and temperature plus  illumination. 20 programs, each consisting of four steps and one  pre-step, can be defined and stored. The menue language can be selected  by the user. CERTOMAT Tplus units can be stacked three units high in  order to save valuable lab space. Due to the patented adjustable mass  compensation system, all three stacked units can be run at maximum speed  even when fully loaded.</p>\r\n<h3>Obligatory Shaker Accessories</h3>\r\n<p>To make it functional,  every CERTOMAT&reg; shaker or incubation shaker requires a tray. Available  tray sizes are 420 x 420 mm (E/EU) and 800 x 420 mm (F/FU). Suitable  trays, clamps and further accessories are listed with each instrument.</p>\r\n</div>','<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"530\" height=\"120\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interior dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>89 x 65 x 49,5 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Orbital shaking amplitude</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>25 mm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stacking</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Up to 3 units without speed reduction</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>650 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cooling capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>500 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Accuracy</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Max. &plusmn;1 % of final value</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line voltage</str