	(47,'SI Series Benchtop Incubation Shaker','<p>Combines a bench-top incubator with dual-action shaking system (orbital  and reciprocal motion). Each model fulfills a variety of molecular  biology, general incubation, and cell culture applications.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>+5&#8451; above room temperature to 60&#8451; for SI-300, 600</li>\r\n<li>15&#8451; to 60&#8451; for SI-300R, 600R</li>\r\n<li>Microprocess PID control/ Auto-tuning/ Calibration.</li>\r\n<li>Digital timer: 1 min to 99 hr 59 min, delayed ON/ OFF.</li>\r\n<li>Select between orbital or reciprocating action.</li>\r\n<li>Speed range: 10 to 300 rpm.</li>\r\n<li>Programmable shaking motion.</li>\r\n<li>Run time: 10 sec to 999 hr 59 min 59 sec.</li>\r\n<li>Forward &amp; Backward, Pause: 10 sec to 59 min 59 sec</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/si_incubation_shakers.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"607\" height=\"247\" /></p>','SHI_Medline_Benchtop_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(48,'Medline Chamber Incubation Shakers','<p>Space- saving design, provides various locations on/under your lab benches, or units can be double-stacked on the Floor<br />Two adjustable-height shelves provide added incubating or storage samples.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>+5&#8451; above room temperature to 80&#8451; for SIF-5000/6000</li>\r\n<li>-20&#8451; above room temperature to 80&#8451; for SIF-5000R/6000R</li>\r\n<li>Microprocessor PID control / Auto-tuning / Calibration</li>\r\n<li>9 step temperature and up to 200 cycles of repetition programmable for each profile</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable fan speed within 3 steps and defrosting time / period control</li>\r\n<li>Select between orbital or reciprocating action.</li>\r\n<li>Speed range: 10 to 300 rpm. (Stackable Top :10 to 250)</li>\r\n<li>Programmable shaking motion.</li>\r\n<li>Run time: 10 sec to 999 hr 59 min 59 sec.</li>\r\n<li>Forward &amp; Backward, Pause: 10 sec to 59 min 50 sec.</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/medline_incubation_shaking_cabinet_main__age.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"599\" height=\"247\" /></p>','SHI_Medline_Chamber_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(49,'Floorstanding Incubation Shakers','<p>Large and heavy capacity shaking with rapid heating / cooling performance.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Advanced shaking for heavy workload and flask up to maximum 4&times;6L.</li>\r\n<li> Exclusive drive mechanism delivers years of dependable service.</li>\r\n<li> +5&#8451; above room temperature to 60&#8451; for IS-971</li>\r\n<li>+4&#8451; to 60&#8451; for IS-971R</li>\r\n<li>Amb. -15&#8451; to 60&#8451; for IS-971R.</li>\r\n<li> Microprocessor PID control/ Auto-tuning/ Calibration.</li>\r\n<li> 9 step temperature and up to 200 cycles of repetition programmable for each profile.</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable 3 step fan speed with defrosting time / period control.</li>\r\n<li> Select between orbital or reciprocating action.</li>\r\n<li> Speed range: 10 to 300 rpm.</li>\r\n<li> Programmable shaking motion.</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/medline_floorstanding_incubation_shakers_main_image.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"577\" height=\"238\" /></p>','SHI_Medline_Floorstanding_Main_Image.jpg'),
