	(56,'CERTOMAT CS-20','<p>CO<sub>2</sub> incubator CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> CS-20 is a state-of-  the-art incubator with a chamber volume of 210 L. Its stainless steel  surfaces in the chamber are doted with copper. In combination with the  integrated UV lamp, which automatically switches on after the door has  been opened and closed, the risk of contamination is efficiently  reduced. This reduces down-time caused by the need for disinfection. The  CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> CS-20 CO<sub>2</sub> incubator is equipped with an IR sensor with a ceramic heater. Together with a PID controller this ensures stable CO<sub>2</sub> concentration and fast recovery after the door has been opened and  closed. Auto-calibration with room air as zero reference prevents CO<sub>2</sub> drift.</p>','<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"437\" height=\"86\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interior dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>66,5 x 52,3 x 66,5 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stacking</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Up to 2 units</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>650 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cooling capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>500 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Accuracy</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Max. &plusmn;1 % of final value</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"744\" height=\"271\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weight (Approx.)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>106 kg</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Housing Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Steel construction</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Connections</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Class I cold socket, separate cable approx. 3 m</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection class</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>I</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection type</strong></t