	(57,'CERTOMAT H','<div class=\"csc-default\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<h3>Description</h3>\r\n<p>The incubation hood CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> H is suited for the  growth of bacteria and yeast cells in a temperature-controlled  environment from 10 &deg;C above ambient to up to +60 &deg;C. The lowest  temperature that can be reached depends on the ambient temperature. The  incubation hood controls the incubation temperature while the bench top  shaker controls the shaking motion. This hood can best be combined with  CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> bench top shakers and a tray of 420 x 420 mm (width x depth).</p>\r\n<h3>Obligatory accessories</h3>\r\n<p>A shaker is required for agitation of the samples.</p>\r\n</div>','<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"550\" height=\"86\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Type</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Incubation hood without port for external cooler</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interior dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>66,8 x 60 x 42 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stacking</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>500 W</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Accuracy</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Max. &plusmn; 6% of final value</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"682\" height=\"339\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weight (Approx.)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>20 kg</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Housing Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Acrylic</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Connections</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Class I cold socket, separate cable approx. 3 m</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection class</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>I</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection type</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>IP21</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n