	(59,'Medline Hotplate and Hot-plate Stirrers','<p>Stylish and economical general purpose hotplate stirrers designed  with safety as well as performance in mind. The compact shape takes up  less bench space and makes storage easier. Medline offers a  comprehensive range of hotplates and stirrers. All have simple analogue  controls and are available with a chemically resistant ceramic 180x180mm  surface platform.</p>\r\n<p><br /> The surface is easy to clean and the thermal properties allow  very high plate temperatures while ensuring the edges stay cooler,  reducing the chance of accidental burns. The white surface ensures good  visibility of colour changes.<br /> All models have an integral fitting for a retort rod.</p>','<table border=\"0\" width=\"402\" height=\"41\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Case construction</strong></td>\r\n<td>Steel, with chemical resistant coating</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stage Area:</strong></td>\r\n<td>180 x 180mm</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Temperature</strong></td>\r\n<td>Up to 400&deg;C (Max)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Speed Range</strong></td>\r\n<td>100 ~ 1500 rpm (stirrer models only)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Power Supply</strong></td>\r\n<td>220V AC</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong></strong><br /><strong></strong> <img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/medline_hot_plates_stirrers_main_image.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"413\" height=\"166\" /><br /><strong></strong><br /><br /></p>\r\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" class=\"mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;\"><strong>Stage Area:</strong></div>','SST_Hot_Plate_Stirrer_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(60,'Medline Magnetic Stirrers','<p><strong>Constructional Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ergonomic design, lightweight, simple to use adn efficient low profile structure</li>\r\n<li>120mm (MS-12B), 170mm and 220 mm included top plate provided</li>\r\n<li>The white and black silicon rubber feet prevent samplefrom slidng</li>\r\n<li>BLCD is less noisy and more durable than regular DC motors/</li>\r\n<li>Best in the class with broad range of RPM speed is reliable</li>\r\n<li>Bult in thermal shutdown and current limit protection.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Additional MS-G Type Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Microprocessor PID controls.</li>\r\n<li>Convenietn program and timer modes</li>\r\n<li>Bright and vivid VFD display and responsive touch screen</li>\r\n<li>Included M12 rod holder from clamping in samples</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Multipositiion Type Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>User friendly and timer mode alllows the user to select from one point on one row or one point in one column, one rwo. one cloumn, or multiple rows and collumns, with different rpm and timer settings,</li>\r\n<li>Easy to read digital VFD control display anad beautifully illuminated LED single position, multiple position, row position and column position lighting. </li>\r\n<li>Non-slip see throug silicon place mat (optional)</li>\r\n<li>Uncompromisisng safety devices</li>\r\n<li>Supported various number of multi-position stirring to meet user demands.</li>\r\n<li>#304 grade stainless steel and chemical resistant top-plate.</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/medline_magnetic_stirrers_main_page.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"565\" height=\"668\" /></p>','SST_Magnetic_Stirrers_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(61,'Medline Stirrer Mantles','<p>These units have a stepless speed control&nbsp;from 100 up&nbsp;to 1200 rpm  with seperate heater control. A Flexible heating element ensures minimum  risk of flask breakage.</p>\r\n<p>These controlled and grounded mantles feature a built-in power regulator and safety earth (ground) screen. <br /> The replaceable coiled heating element is suspended within a thermal  insulating cartridge to provide maximum heat transfer and support. Glass  fibre insulation coupled with excellent ventilation helps to keep the  outer aluminium casing cool. Built-in power controller has dial markings  from 1 to 10 for excellent repeatability.</p>\r\n<p>Medline E-Series Mantles feature indicator lights: a green coloured  \"power-on\" light (and switch) with an amber coloured \"heater-on\" light.  The stainless steel grounding screen provides added protection against  shock in the event of spillage or flask breakage. Available sizes are  from 50ml up to 20,000ml.</p>','<table border=\"0\" width=\"371\" height=\"42\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Case Construction</strong></td>\r\n<td>Steel, with chemical resistant coating</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Thermal Insulation</strong></td>\r\n<td>Moulded silica powder</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating Element</strong></td>\r\n<td>Nichrome wire</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Mantle</strong></td>\r\n<td>Woven glass fibre mat</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Element Temperature</strong></td>\r\n<td>Up to 450&deg;C (Max)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Speed Range</strong></td>\r\n<td>100 ~ 1000 rpm</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Power Supply</strong></td>\r\n<td>220V AC</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>','BTE_Stirrer_Mantles_Main_Image.jpg'),
