	(66,'CERTOMAT R','<div class=\"csc-default\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<h3>Description</h3>\r\n<p>Benchtop shaker CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> R is a shaker with two  outstanding features, due to its strong magnetic drive: Extremely low  running noise and long service life without maintenance. The CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> R benchtop shaker is equipped with an acoustic alarm and a memory function for automatic re-start after power failure.</p>\r\n<h3>Obligatory Shaker Accessories</h3>\r\n<p>To make it functional,  every CERTOMAT&reg; shaker or incubation shaker requires a tray. Available  tray sizes are 420 x 420 mm (E/EU) and 800 x 420 mm (F/FU). Suitable  trays, clamps and further accessories are listed with each instrument.</p>\r\n</div>','<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"494\" height=\"123\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interior dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Depending on tray, mounting system and other accessories</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Adjustable mass compensation</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>No</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stacking</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cooling capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Accuracy</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Max. &plusmn;5 % of final value</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line voltage</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>230 V</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"606\" height=\"349\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line frequency</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>50 Hertz</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>External Width</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>48 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>External Height</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>10 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr