	(67,'CERTOMAT U','<div class=\"csc-default\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<h3>Description</h3>\r\n<p>Benchtop shaker CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> U is identical to the CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> R benchtop shaker in all features, but its movement can be converted  from orbital to longitudinal shaking. While orbital shaking is preferred  for cultivating all kinds of cells, linear shaking can be used for  destaining of electrophoresis gels, for extraction purposes and others.  This makes the CERTOMAT<sup>&reg;</sup> U benchtop shaker an extremely flexible tool for lab work.</p>\r\n<h3>Obligatory Shaker Accessories</h3>\r\n<p>To make it functional,  every CERTOMAT&reg; shaker or incubation shaker requires a tray. Available  tray sizes are 420 x 420 mm (E/EU) and 800 x 420 mm (F/FU). Suitable  trays, clamps and further accessories are listed with each instrument.</p>\r\n</div>','<table class=\"contenttable\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interior dimensions (WxDxH)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Depending on tray, mounting system and other accessories</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Adjustable mass compensation</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>No</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Stacking</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Heating capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cooling capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>none</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Accuracy</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Max. &plusmn;5 % of final value</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line voltage</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>115 V</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Line frequency</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>60 Hertz</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>External Width</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>48 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>External Height</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>13 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>External Depth</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>52 cm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Recommended trays</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Type E|EU (420 + 420 mm), Type F|FU (800 + 420 mm)</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Tray fixation</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Fixation lever</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Maximum load</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>20 kg</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Connections</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Class I cold socket, separate cable approx. 3 m</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Protection class</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>I</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Fuses</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>2 x T2 A at 230 V, 2 x T2.5 A at 115 V</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Interference</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>According to DIN EN 55022 and DIN EN 61000</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Mode</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Orbital/linear (convertible)</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Amplitude</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>25 mm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Shaking speed</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>40 - 350 rpm / 40 - 200 rpm</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Display</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>LED</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Memory</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Restart after power failure</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Alarms</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Acoustic</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Relative humidity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Avoid extreme humidity</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Housing Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Steel construction</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weight</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>52 kg</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','SST_Ce