	(104,'BS-Series Shaking and Heating Baths','<p><strong>Shaking and Heating Baths</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Operational Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>+5 C above room temperature to 100 C</li>\r\n<li>Microprocess PID control/ built-in calibration</li>\r\n<li>Digital timer: 1 in to 99 hr 59 min, delayed ON/OFF.</li>\r\n<li>Independent over-temperature limiter.</li>\r\n<li>Digital LED display</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Constructional Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong></strong>Shalker mechanism has its own control keys, so the unti can be used as constant temperature baths.</li>\r\n<li>Gently start shaking to minimize shock to the test sample</li>\r\n<li>Multi-LED display for adjusting actual value setpoint temperatures and shaking frequency.</li>\r\n<li>Baffle plate screens circulator, heater, and sensor to minimize turbulence in the bath fluid and to protect the sample and the user from direct contact with the bath fluid.</li>\r\n<li>Included bath coover prevents liquid losses, the gable type roof ensures no dripping into the test sample directly.</li>\r\n<li>Included SUS 304 spring wire rack consists double column for various setting of glassware.</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/shaking_heating_baths.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"196\" /></p>','LWE_Medline_SHaking_bath_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(105,'Bath and Circulator Accessories','<p><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>For Shaking and Heating Baths</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Universal platform and Flask Clamps</strong></p>\r\n<p>The universal platforms provide flexibility for mixing different size test tubes and glassware on a single platfrom.&nbsp; Available with different size clamps for Erlenmeyer flasks.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dedicated platforms</strong></p>\r\n<p>If using a single flask size only, the dedicated platform can be sude. Comes with the clamp installed.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Test Tube Racks</strong></p>\r\n<p>Highly durable stainless steel racks with adjustable angle and height support.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>For Baths and Bath Circulators</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Transparent polypropylene gable type covers</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pevnet liquid floss due to evaporation, protect samples from contamination made of transparent polypropence materials.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stainless Steel flat type covers</strong></p>\r\n<p>Made of stainless steel to prevent corrosion and rust.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Open-rings covers</strong></p>\r\n<p>Beaker or Erlenmeyer flask can be placed directly onto the perforated stainless steel half-shelf adjuster or water tanks. Adjustable rings size for each glassware to minimize liquid due to evaporation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Test tube racks</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hghly durable stainless steel racks with adjustable angle and height support.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Spring Wire Racks</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ideal for holding a wide variety of tubes, flasks, and other glassware. All components are made of stainless steel.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Suction functon for pumps.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Additional suction function for powerful external/internal circulating. Maximum suction flow rate 10.0 liters per minute.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Half-Shelf Adjusters</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stainless steel perforated sample tray shelf with adjustable height support prevents leaks an