les_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(120,'Combics Complete Scale','<p>With the Combics product family, Sartorius offers a high-quality  scale series for the various applications of the food, pharmaceutical,  chemical, metal and electrical industries. <br />Combics can adjust  optimally to different process requirements due to its high flexibility  regarding connection and configuration options.<br /><br />Combics complete  scales come combined with platforms and indicators already installed and  ready for use. Multiple combination options ensure the highest degree  of individuality.<br />Our Combics Configurator supports the selection and ordering process.<br /><br />Combics  industrial scales have everything you need. They offer a high  protection class up to IP 69K, ATEX certifications as well as various  accessories in different material versions such as printers, roller  conveyors, benches, frames for pit installations or drive-on ramps.</p>\r\n<p>For more details on product specifications and model selection please press the button \"Product-Configurator\".</p>\r\n<h3>Weighing platforms</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Painted and stainless steel versions available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Very  robust in aggressive environments due to high corrosion and IP  protection (stainless steel versions up to V4A | 1.4571, electropolished  and IP68 |IP69K)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Optimally customized to the area of application due to 10 weighing ranges from 3 kg to 3 t and 13 platform dimensions </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Precision up to 30,000d when not used in legal metrology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>When used in legal metrology up to 6000e and/or 3 x 3000e (multi-range and multi-interval possible)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>High resolution weighing platforms</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Area of application from 16 kg to 300 kg in various platform dimensions </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Precision up to 340,000d when not used in legal metrology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>When used in legal metrology class II up to 34,000e </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>With internal motorized calibration weight</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Indicators</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Flexibility due to 9 application programs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>User-friendly due to clear text displays, bar graph, control light fields</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Easy integration due to standardized data interfaces, e.g. RS232, Profibus DP, Ethernet TCP/IP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>For use in legal metrology applications up to 10,000e, optional integrated Alibi memory</li>\r\n</ul>','<table border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong> <br /></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;3-3,000 kg <br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Max. Readability </strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Verifiable: 1x6000e,1x3000e,2x3000e,3x3000e</p>\r\n<p>Non-verificable: 15,000d,30,0000d</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Material </strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Painted (IP65) or Stainless steel (IP68, IP69K as option)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Size</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Refer to table below</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Indicator </strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>3 Selection (Refer to table below)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Operating Temperature Range </strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;-10 to 40 Centigrade.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Indicator Selection</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/combics_complete_sclae_indicator.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"603\" height=\"552\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Platform Selection</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/combics_platform.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"597\" height=\"363\" /><br /></strong></p>','CS_Combics_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(121,'Signum Complete Scale','<p>The new Signum&reg; industrial scale from Sartorius is a compact  industrial scale in which a choice of two powerful technologies is used:  SIWR and SIWA models work with a strain-gauge type load cell; the  high-resolution SIWS models feature monolithic weigh cells based on  electromagnetic force compensation. The new Signum&reg; offers exceptional  performance features and, despite its wide variety of functions, is a  very easy-to-operate industrial scale. The Signum&reg; is extremely rugged  and resistant, and perfectly adapts to any ambient conditions in an  industrial environment.</p>\r\n<p>With Signum&reg; industrial scale, anything  is possible: pick and choose your level of applications and different  resolutions, and enjoy the benefits of a wide variety of interfaces and  options for use in hazardous areas and for many more features. The  Signum&reg; is a compact scale built exactly the way you want it - without  compromises.</p>\r\n<p>With the high resolution versions of the Signum&reg;  series you can realize resolutions in the milligram range. They are  especially designed for precise weighing tasks and applications such as  counting, checking and formulation.</p>\r\n<p>For more details on product specifications and model selection please press the button \"Product-Configurator\".</p>','<table border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Signum Regular :3-60 kg</p>\r\n<p>Sginum Advanced : 7 - 65 kg</p>\r\n<p>Signum Supreme: 3 - 35 kg</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Readability</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Signum Regular: up to 35,000d</p>\r\n<p>Signum Advance:up tp 65,000d</p>\r\n<p>Signum Supreme up to 350,000d</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Size</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Signum Series : 350 x 240 mm.</p>\r\n<p>Signum Supreme Stainless Steel : 182 x 182 mm or 370 x 260 mm</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Signum Series : IP44 (Stainless Platform with Painted Steel body)</p>\r\n<p>Signum Supreme Stainless Steel : IP65 (Full Stainless Steel)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Indicator</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>3 Selection, Please refer to table below</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Indicator Selection</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/signum_indicator.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"509\" /><br /></strong></p>','CS_Signum_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(122,'Midrics Compete Scale','<p>There are hundreds of possible applications for an industrial scale,  and not everyone needs a standard \"off-the-rack\" solution. Whatever,  wherever, and however the Midrics&reg; industrial scale can do it all:</p>\r\n<p>You  can order a complete scale, individual configurations, or separate  modules. From 0.2 g to 3 t, verified or non-verified, with or without EX  protection, Zone 2 and 22.</p>','<table border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong></td>\r\n<td>3 - 3,000 kg</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Max. Readability</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>verifiable : 3,000e, 2x3000e</p>\r\n<p>Non-verifiable : 15,000d</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Indicator : Stainless Steel (IP65)</p>\r\n<p>Platform : Painted Steel (IP65) or Stainless Steel (IP67)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Operating Temperature</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>-10 to 40 Centigrade</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Size</strong></td>\r\n<td>Multiple, Please see table below</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Indicator </strong></td>\r\n<td>2 Selection, please see below</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Indicator Selection</strong></p>\r\n<div><strong>Midrics&reg; Scale Indicator MIS 1</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Display: backlit, 14-segment, 20 mm LCD for weight readouts</li>\r\n<li>Optional RS-232, RS-485, RS-422, 4-20mA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><strong>Midrics&reg; Scale Indicator MIS2</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Display: backlit, 14-segment, 20 mm LCD for weight readouts, bar graph</li>\r\n<li>Connection for bar code scanner; battery operation</li>\r\n<li>Optional RS-232, RS-485, RS-422, 4-20mA, Digital I/O</li>\r\n<li>Applications: weighing, counting, checkweighing, classification (into three or five classes), totalizing, net-total, weighing in percent, neutral measurement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Platform Selection</strong><