	(176,'Wire Weights','<p>Individual E1 class weights from 1mg to 500 mg. Material: special steel,  non-magnetizable, density 8.0 g/cm3, highly corrosion-resistant, in  plastic case.</p>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/wire_weight.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"535\" height=\"431\" /></p>','WGT_WIre_Weights_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(177,'Knob Weights','<p>Individual E1, E2, F1, F2 and M1 OIML class weights. The special steel  knob weights are highly polished, corrosion-resistant and available from  1 g to 50 kg. They are non-magnetisable and have a density of 8.0 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. Packaged in a plastic case (up to 20 g) or a wooden case (from 50 g) the knob weights are comfortably to store.</p>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/knob_weight.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"502\" height=\"477\" /></p>','WGT_Knob_Weights.jpg'),
	(178,'Leaf Weights','<p>Individual F1 OIML class weights, made of aluminimum or nickel silver.  The aluminum leaf weights are available from 1 mg to 5 mg and have a  density of  2.7 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. The nickel silver leaf weights can be ordered from 10 mg to 500 mg and feature a density of  8.7 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. Packaged in a plastic case the leaf weights are comfortably to store.</p>','<h3>Product properties</h3>\r\n<table class=\"contenttable\" width=\"307\" height=\"63\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Accuracy class acc. to OIML R111</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>F1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Nominal mass value</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>1 mg - 500mg</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>DAkkS certificate</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Yes</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','WGT_Leaf_Weights_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(179,'Block Shaped Weights','<p>Individual block shaped M1 and M2 OIML class weights. The weights are  made of black painted grey cast . You can order the block shapped  weights from 5 kg to 50 kg.</p>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/block_shaped_weights.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"337\" /></p>','WGT_Block_Shaped_Weights_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(180,'Weight Sets','<p>Individual E1, E2, F1, F2 and M1 OIML class weight sets. The sets are  made of highly polished special steel, nickel silver, galvanised brass  or aluminium. Choose from weight sets including wire weights, leaf  weights or knob weights from 1 g to 50 kg.</p>','<p><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/weught_set.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"498\" /></p>','WGT_Weights_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(181,'Steel Truck Scale Weighing Platform','<p>The truck scale steel weighing platform is a highly robust weighing platform design for truck weighing. Made of high-strength steel the platform is designed to withstand high-frequency of use. Its modular design enables us to quickly assemble the platform on-site. The design of the platform is modifiable depending on user requirement however, we have a standard design available that has been tested its strength and quality.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advantages of Steel Weighbridge Platform</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The total weight of the platfrom is much lighter thatn its adversaries, the concrete platform, therefore you can have more weighing capacity given the same platform size if compared to a concrete platform.</li>\r\n<li>Its modular design enables quick installation, the construction requires less time since it arrives at the client site in modules.</li>\r\n<li>Depending on the condition of the platform, it might be possible to dismantle and relocate the weighbridge. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Type of Weighbridge Platform Available (Based on Type)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/weighbridge_type.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"457\" height=\"255\" /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>','<table border=\"0\" width=\"523\" height=\"90\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Capacity(Tons)</strong></td>\r\n<td>Depend on customer requirement<br />Standard: 40,60,80</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Size(m)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depend on customer requirement<br />Standard: 3x9,3x12,3x15,3x18</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>High-strength steel, painted or sandblast coating</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong># of Load Cells</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depending on capacity and size</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Foundation Type</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depending on soil condition on site.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Steel Weighbridge Platform.jpg'),
	(182,'Concrete Truck Scale Weighing Platform','<p>The concrete truck scale weighing platform offers you a high-quality and solid foundation intended for heavy duty weighing. The whole platfrom is made from a single solid casting, wnsuring high durability and accuracy weighing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advantages of Concrete Truck Scale Weighing Platform</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Concrete weighing platform is more resistant to corrosion compared to steel weighing platform</li>\r\n<li>Concrete weighing platform has longer lifetime especially especially if subjected to very large weight. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Available Platform Style (Based on Type)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/panatrade/uploads/images/weighbridge_type.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"261\" /><br /></strong></p>','<table border=\"0\" width=\"523\" height=\"90\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Capacity(Tons)</strong></td>\r\n<td>Depend on customer requirement<br />Standard: 40,60,80</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Size(m)</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depend on customer requirement<br />Standard: 3x9,3x12,3x15,3x18</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Platform Material</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>ConcreteHigh-strength steel, painted or sandblast coating</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong># of Load Cells</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depending on capacity and size</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Foundation Type</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depending on soil condition on site.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Concrete Truck Scale Weighing Platform.jpg'),
	(183,'Bacti Burner','<p>The Medline Bacti-Burner is designed for &ldquo;on the bench&rdquo; sterilization  of research microbiology tools. It has an asbestos-free core element  that uses infrared heating to produce 815&deg;C (1500&deg;F). It completely  sterilizes microorganisms within 5-7 seconds and provides instant  sterilization of platinum inoculating loops, needles, glass tube/pipette  mouths and various metal &amp; borosilicate glass instruments, commonly  used in microbiology research</p>\r\n<p>The ceramic heating element is safely enclosed in a perforated  stainless steel guard chamber, protecting users from accidental contact  with the extreme temperatures of the core area. It is extremely compact,  convenient and can be used in anaerobic and aerobic chambers.</p>','','BTE_Bacti_Burner_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(184,'Software (Mass Comparator)','<h1>Application software for mass metrology<span> YPR02C</span></h1>\r\n<p>This software permits determination of the differences between two  masses as well as determination of absolute masses or apparent masses  (conventional mass), allowing for air buoyancy errors. It is designed  for automatic logging of data transmitted by Sartorius mass comparators  and for control of automatic mass comparators with a load alternator.  Using in conjunction with a Sartorius climate station, YPR02C is  suitable for continuous climate data recording.</p>\r\n<h1>SartoCollect, software for data communication with the PC</h1>\r\n<p>The standard data communications software for Sartorius instruments (balances/scales, moisture analyzer and pH-meter). Connecting cable must be ordered separately.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Data transfer into a PC </li>\r\n<li>Direct data integration in MS EXCEL, WORD, ACCESS or an ASCII file </li>\r\n<li>Keyboard emulation (wedge function) for data integration in an active application (e.g. SAP or LIMS system) </li>\r\n<li>Direct interface to database applications (e.g. SQL server) </li>\r\n<li>Instruments (manufacturer independent) can be connected via RS232, RS422, RS485, Bluetooth, or TCP/IP. </li>\r\n<li>Integrated VBA Script Editor for advanced applications </li>\r\n<li>Up to 99 instruments can be connected/operated at the same time and the data can be transferred into one EXCEL sheet </li>\r\n<li>Integrated instrument library with preconfigured instruments (manufacturer independent) </li>\r\n<li>Easy \"Step by Step\" configuration </li>\r\n<li>Finished configurations are stored as methods and are easy and fast accessible </li>\r\n<li>7 languages are available (ge, en, it, fr, es, ru, jp) </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>ScalesNet-M basic module<span> YSN03C</span></h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>','','COM_Software.jpg'),
