	(204,'Proline Plus Mechanical Pipette','<p>The Proline Plus pipette family offers a wide variety of both fixed  and variable volume models as well as unique combination of novel and  patented features. High quality and light pipetting forces provide  pleasant pipetting experience. The Proline Plus with robust design is  suitable for variable every day laboratory applications. <br /><br />The Proline Plus pipettors cover the full range of 0.1&micro;l to 10ml.<br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Key Benefits:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Reduced pipetting forces prevent RSI and improve the results </li>\r\n<li>Accurate and precise</li>\r\n<li>Contamination free pipetting with Safe-Cone Filters </li>\r\n<li>Robust design</li>\r\n<li>Easiest pipette to maintain</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Robust yet light and easy to use </li>\r\n<li>High chemical and UV resistance </li>\r\n<li>Fully autoclavable </li>\r\n<li>Optiload mechanism, originally developed by Biohit,&nbsp;in multichannel models for perfect tip sealing </li>\r\n<li>Volume setting by click stops </li>\r\n<li>Suitable for both left and right-handed </li>\r\n<li>Compatible with a wide range of tips </li>\r\n<li>Compatible with most commonly used lab tubes due to slim tip ejector collar </li>\r\n<li>Safe-Cone Filter to prevent contamination and damage of pipette </li>\r\n<li>Volume range colour-coding for easy pipette and tip selection </li>\r\n<li>Only 2-3 parts to disassemble and clean </li>\r\n<li>CE/IVD marked</li>\r\n<li>3-year warranty </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Item</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Channels</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Increment</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Test volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Inaccuracy</td>\r\n<td sty