	(206,'mLINE Starter Kit','<p>Biohit mLINE Starter Kit offers an opportunity to test and get started  with mLINE pipettes. You can choose between two Starter Kits with three  single-channel mLINE pipettes. <br /><br />Both kits also include color  coded Optifit Tip racks for every pipette and many useful accessories  such as pipette holder, colour coding caps and a calibration tool, which  also acts as a tube opener.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Biohit mLINE Starter Kit 1</span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> mLINE pipette 0.5-10 &micro;l </li>\r\n<li>mLINE pipette 10-100 &micro;l</li>\r\n<li><span>mLINE pipette 100-1000 </span>&micro;l</li>\r\n<li>Pipette Holder x 3</li>\r\n<li>Colour Coding Caps</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Pen</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Optifit Tip 0.2-10 &micro;l, Single Tray</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Optifit Tip 0.5-300 &micro;l, Single Tray</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Optifit Tip 10-1000 &micro;l, Single Tray</li>\r\n<li>Calibration Tool/Tube Opener</li>\r\n<li>Literature</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Biohit mLINE Starter Kit 2</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>mLINE pipette 2-20 &micro;l</li>\r\n<li>mLINE pipette 20-200 &micro;l</li>\r\n<li>mLINE pipette 100-1000 &micro;l</li>\r\n<li>Pipette Holder x 3</li>\r\n<li>Colour Coding Caps</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Pen</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Optifit Tip 0.5-300 &micro;l, Single Tray x 2</li>\r\n<li>Biohit Optifit Tip 10-1000 &micro;l, Single Tray</li>\r\n<li>Calibration Tool/Tube Opener</li>\r\n<li>Literature</li>\r\n</ul>','MPT_mLINE_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(207,'mLINE PCR Starter Kit','<p>mLINE PCR Starter Kit offers an easy start in PCR application. The fully autoclavable mLINE pipettes and sterile Biohit SafetySpace<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&trade;</span> Filter Tips guarantee contamination free pipetting. The kits also incluce a cooling rack for microtubes, a cryo pen and other accessories. <br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">mLINE - the promise of lighter liquid handling</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Effortless accuracy and precision</li>\r\n<li>Fully autoclavable</li>\r\n<li>Easy maintenance and calibration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">SafetySpace&trade; Filter Tips - safer pipetting and better accuracy</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>More space between sample and filter</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">PCR- Starter Kit includes &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>mLINE 0.5-10 &micro;l single-channel pipette</li>\r\n<li>mLINE 10-100 &micro;l single-channel pipette</li>\r\n<li>mLINE 100-1000 &micro;l single-channel pipette</li>\r\n<li>SafetySpace 10 &micro;l Filter Tip rack, sterile</li>\r\n<li>SafetySpace 120 &micro;l Filter Tip rack, sterile</li>\r\n<li>SafetySpace 1000 &micro;l Filter Tip rack, sterile</li>\r\n<li>Pipette holder, 3 pcs</li>\r\n<li>Micro tube opener/Calibration tool, 3 pcs</li>\r\n<li>Colour coding caps</li>\r\n<li>Cryo pen (black)</li>\r\n<li>Aluminium cooling rack for 12 micro tubes</li>\r\n</ul>','MPT_mLINE_PCR_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(208,'Proline Plus Starter Kit','<p>Biohit Proline&reg; Plus Starter Kit offers an opportunity to test and get started with Proline Plus pipettes. You can choose between four Starter Kits with two or three single-channel Proline Plus pipettes. <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /><br /></span>All kits also include color coded Optifit Tip racks for every pipette  and many useful accessories such as pipette holders  and a calibration tool, which also acts as a tube opener.</p>','<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Biohit Proline Plus Starter Kit 1<br /><br /></span>&bull; Proline Plus 0.1 - 3 &mu;l<br />&bull; Proline Plus 0.5 -10 &mu;l<br />&bull; Pipette Holder x 2<br />&bull; 2 single-tray tip boxes<br />&bull; Calibration Tool/Tube Opener<br />&bull; Literature <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /><br style=\"font-weight: bold;\" />Biohit Proline Plus Starter Kit 2 </span><br /><br />&bull; Proline Plus 0.5 - 10 &mu;l<br />&bull; Proline Plus 10 - 100 &mu;l<br />&bull; Proline Plus 100-1000 &mu;l<br />&bull; Pipette Holder x 3<br />&bull; 3 single-tray tip boxes<br />&bull; Calibration Tool/Tube Opener<br />&bull; Literature  <br /><br /> <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Biohit Proline Plus Starter Kit</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3</span><br /><br />&bull; Proline Plus 2 - 20 &mu;l<br />&bull; Proline Plus 20 - 200 &mu;l<br />&bull; Proline Plus 100 - 1000 &mu;l<br />&bull; Pipette Holder x 3<br />&bull; 3 single-tray tip boxes<br />&bull; Calibration Tool/Tube Opener<br />&bull; Literature  <br /><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Biohit Proline Plus Starter Kit 4 </span><br /><br />&bull; Proline Plus 500-5000 &mu;l<br />&bull; Proline Plus 1000-10 000 &mu;l<br />&bull; Pipette Holder x 2<br />&bull; 2 bulk tip boxes<br />&bull; Calibration Tool/Tube Opener<br />&bull; Literature</p>','MPT_Proline_Plus_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(209,'Picus Electronic Pipette','<p>Meet Picus &ndash; the Red Dot awarded electronic pipette that eases your  work load, protects you from injuries by ensuring optimal working  posture and allows accurate and precise pipetting results!<br /> <br /> Known as forerunner in liquid handling products with a long history in  developing ergonomic, high quality pipettes, Biohit has now set a  completely new standard for electronic pipettes. A dedicated team of  R&amp;D and ergonomics professionals, together with laboratory  personnel, has developed a new technology with your needs and well being  in mind. The result is the most ergonomic and sophisticated pipette in  the market for laboratory professionals who demand the highest quality,  safety and reliability in their work.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ergonomics</strong></p>\r\n<p>Biohit Picus is the smallest and lightest electronic pipette on the  market helping to avoid pipetting caused symptoms like RSI (repetitive  strain injury). Picus handle desing and location of operation buttons  enable comfortable pipetting feeling.<br /> Electronic tip ejection, one hand- operated Adjustment wheel and  conveniently located Start button minimizes the force needed in  pipetting. Repetitive and time consuming pipetting can be done  accurately and fast with serial dispensing modes and a new Tracker &ndash;  great help for example in microplate work.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reliable results</strong></p>\r\n<p>Due to advanced DC-motor concept and built-in error control Biohit  Picus ensures the most accurate and precise pipetting results. Find more  details on specifications under the &ldquo;specifications&rdquo; tab.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key benefits</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Helps you prevent repetitive strain injury (RSI) due to light weight, ergonomic design and electronic tip ejection.</li>\r\n<li> Achieve better and more reliable results with a new generation technology and the error control system.</li>\r\n<li> Save time with an extremely fast one-hand adjustment, a unique built-in microplate tracker and easy programmability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Picus is the smallest and lightest electronic pipette, help to avoid RSI (repetitive strain injury)</li>\r\n<li> Ergonomics is brought to a new level with electronic tip ejection,  adjustment wheel for scrolling menus, adjusting volume and controlling  manual pipetting and feather light operating button</li>\r\n<li> Unbeatable accuracy and precision due to advanced technology. Reliability of results is guaranteed with error control system</li>\r\n<li> Variety of pipetting modes in user friendly interface including memory places for the favorite programs</li>\r\n<li> Unique Tracker in conjunction with pipetting, reverse pipetting and multi dispensing modes to help microplate work</li>\r\n<li> Adjustment possibility for 1-point, 2-points and 3-points</li>\r\n<li> Easy maintenance of lower parts with GLP (Good Laboratory Practice)  information integrated in software for following the service and  calibration</li>\r\n<li> Safe-Cone filters in all models &gt; 10 &micro;l to prevent contaminations</li>\r\n<li> Autoclavable lower parts in all models (excl. mcp 1200 &micro;l)</li>\r\n<li> Compatible with the Biohit electronic pipette charging systems,  charging stand for 1 pipette and charging carousel for 4 pipettes.  Direct charging option with micro USB cable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Item</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Channels</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Increment</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Test volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Inaccuracy</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Imprecision</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Picus