	(210,'eLINE Electronic Pipette','<p>he electronic Biohit eLINE pipette is the market leader in performance  and ergonomics. This award winning (Pro Finnish Design 2001) pipette  takes the effort out of pipetting and significantly reduces the risk of  Repetitive Strain Injury (RSI).<br /> <br /> The comprehensive range of pipetting programs in eLINE reduces the need  for several work stages and enables you to dispense liquids twice as  fast compared to a mechanical pipette. The unique DC-motor concept with  build-in error control improves pipetting precision and allows more  reliable results.<br /> <br /> eLINE is available in single-channel models covering the volume range  of 0.1 to 5000 &mu;l and multichannel models from 0.2 to 1200 &mu;l.<br /> <br /> <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Key benefits:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Excellent accuracy and precision with unique DC motor concept</li>\r\n<li> Fully electronic operations guarantee user-independent results and prevent RSI</li>\r\n<li> Easiest tip ejection ever with the electronic tip ejection</li>\r\n<li> Twice as fast as a mechanical pipette</li>\r\n<li> One eLINE covers the volume range of two mechanical pipettes &ndash; less pipettes needed</li>\r\n<li> Comprehensive range of pipetting programs</li>\r\n<li> Several charging options</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Unbeatable accuracy and precision with <span class=\"cms_video\">unique DC motor concept</span></li>\r\n<li> Fully electronic operations guarantee user-independent results</li>\r\n<li> Patented and built-in <span class=\"cms_video\">error control</span> for more reliable results</li>\r\n<li> The easiest tip ejection ever with the <span class=\"cms_video\">unique electronic tip ejection</span></li>\r\n<li> Ergonomic design that suits both left- and right-handed</li>\r\n<li> <span class=\"cms_video\">Optiload mechanism</span>, originally developed by Biohit, in multichannel models for perfect tip sealing</li>\r\n<li> Easy programming, 6 memory places for favorite programs</li>\r\n<li> Different charging options (charging stand, charging carousel and direct charging)</li>\r\n<li> Single point calibration for special liquids</li>\r\n<li> Autoclavable dispensing heads (excl.1200 &micro;l 8/12 channel models)</li>\r\n<li> Safe Cone Filters to prevent contamination and damage of pipette</li>\r\n<li> 2-year warranty</li>\r\n<li> CE/IVD marked</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Operational Modes</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Pipetting</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Reverse Pipetting</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Super Pipetting</span> *</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Pipetting+Mixing</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Multiple Dispensing</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Diluting</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Diluting+Mixing </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Sequential Dispening</span>&nbsp; **</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"cms_video\">Multi Aspirating</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span class=\"cms_video\">* Only in eLINE 0.1-5 </span><span class=\"cms_video\"> &micro;l</span><br /><span class=\"cms_video\">*</span><span class=\"cms_video\">* Excl. eLINE 0.1-5 &micro;l</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Item</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Channels</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Increment</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Test volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Inaccuracy</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Imprecision</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>eLINE Electronic Pipette</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.2-10 &micro;l</td>\r\n<t