	(214,'Filter Tip, Regular','<p>Filter tips with regular air gap are made of polypropylene. Filter tips are tray-packed, electron beam pre-sterilized and certified as RNase, DNase and endotoxin free.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Reduce the risk of contamination of the pipette or sample</li>\r\n<li>Made of&nbsp; polypropylene (tip) and polyethylene (filter) </li>\r\n<li>Single tray packages, wrapped in air-tight plastic </li>\r\n<li>Electron beam pre-sterilized (red dot) </li>\r\n<li>Non autoclavable </li>\r\n<li>Certified as DNase, RNase and endotoxin free </li>\r\n<li>CE certified </li>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"ordering\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Volume<br /></td>\r\n<td>Item<br /></td>\r\n<td>Package<br /></td>\r\n<td>Quantity<br /></td>\r\n<td>Purity Level<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>0.1 - 10 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>Filter Tip, regular</td>\r\n<td>Single Tray</td>\r\n<td>10 x 96 Tips</td>\r\n<td>Pre-Sterilized</td>\r\n<td class=\"order\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>10-500 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>Filter Tip, regular</td>\r\n<td>Single Tray</td>\r\n<td>10 x 100 Tips</td>\r\n<td>Pre-Sterilized</td>\r\n<td class=\"order\"><span class=\"order\" style=\"border-bottom: medium none;\">&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','PPT_Filter_Tip_Regular_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(215,'eLINE Lite Dispenser','<p>The automated liquid handling operation offers accurate and repetitive  dispensing also with viscous, infectuous and high vapour pressure  liquids. <br /><br />The unique TipGuide selects and displays the most  suitable tip size which saves time and eliminates the possibility of an  incorrect tip selection.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Unique TipGuide for automatic tip selection </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Easy programming, quick and simple to operate&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Contamination free dispensing with positive displacement principle </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Volume range from 1&micro;l to 50ml </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Speed adjustment for aspiration and dispensing </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Unbeatable accuracy &amp; precision thanks to the patented DC-motor&nbsp;concept with built-in error control&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Unique electronic tip ejection, which reduces the RSI (repetitive strain injury) </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Charging indicator </li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2-year warranty</li>\r\n</ul>','<table style=\"width: 554px; height: 224px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">eLINE Dispensenser operating modes</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;eLINE Pro<br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;eLINE Lite&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Multiple Dispensing with the Tip Guide</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">x<br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">x<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Multiple Dispensing</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: cen