	(217,'Biohit Mechanical Stepper','<p>The Biohit Mechanical Stepper is an easy-to-use positive displacement  instrument which allows rapid multi-dispensing of pre-set volumes up to  48 times in succession without refilling.</p>\r\n<p>The unit comes complete with an adapter for 25 ml and 50 ml syringes.</p>\r\n<p>The Biohit Mechanical Stepper is compatible with various syringe brands.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Easy single handed operation </li>\r\n<li>Lightweight (105 g) yet robust construction </li>\r\n<li>Maintenance-free design </li>\r\n<li>Compatible with a wide range of dispenser tips </li>\r\n<li>Ideal for dispensing aqueous and viscous liquids </li>\r\n<li>Dispensing volumes from 1 &micro;l to 5000 &micro;l (min. volume with Biohit Dispenser Tip is 2 &micro;l) </li>\r\n<li>Ergonomic design and positioning of the dosage button in the upper  part of the device allow single-handed volume selection, loading and  dispensing. </li>\r\n<li>Tested according to ISO 8655-1</li>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Tip volume (ml)</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">Dosage volume</td>\r\n<td>Imprecision (%)</td>\r\n<td>Inaccuracy (%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\">\r\n<td>Adjustement on dispenser<br /></td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>2</td>\r\n<td>3</td>\r\n<td>4</td>\r\n<td>5</td>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\">\r\n<td>number of steps<br /></td>\r\n<td>48</td>\r\n<td>23</td>\r\n<td>15</td>\r\n<td>11</td>\r\n<td>8</td>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>0.10</td>\r\n<td>2 &micro;l<br /></td>\r\n<td>4 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>6 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>8 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>10 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>&lt; 1.6 %<br /></td>\r\n<td>&lt; &plusmn; 3.0 %<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>0.20</td>\r\n<td>4 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>8 &micro;l</td>\r\n<td>12 &micro;l</td