	(220,'Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser','<p>The easy-to-use Prospensers deliver trouble-free and reliable dispensing of liquids including strong acids, bases and solvents.<br /><br />All  models are fitted with an anti-drip safety valve, a feature which  guards against drips when the Prospenser is not in use. A fine  adjustment mechanism allows even greater reproducibility for repeat  dispensing. The Prospenser features easy-to-adjust calibration  mechanism.<br /><br />Unlike other bottle-top dispensers, Prospenser&rsquo;s glass  barrel can be disassembled from the pedestal for thorough cleaning.  This also ensures that in the unlikely event of damage the glass barrel  can be replaced as a spare part.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dispensing directly from the supply bottle</li>\r\n<li>Easy to adjust calibration mechanism</li>\r\n<li>Fully autoclavable at 121&#730;C , 2 bar, 20 minutes</li>\r\n<li>Accuracy of delivery within &plusmn;0.3% on maximum delivery</li>\r\n<li>Chemically resistant fluid pathway</li>\r\n<li>Anti-drip precision valve mechanism ensures easy priming and minimum waste with no leakage back into the reservoir</li>\r\n<li>Easy to use volume adjustment for reproducible dispensings</li>\r\n<li>Unlike other bottle-top dispensers, Prospenser&rsquo;s glass barrel can be disassembled from the pedestal for thorough cleaning</li>\r\n<li>Wide range of adapters are included to fit the most common bottle sizes</li>\r\n<li>Optional dispense tube extention allows fast and safe dispensing even to narrow tubes</li>\r\n<li>Manufactured to ISO9001 standards </li>\r\n<li>Each unit is supplied with an individual calibration certificate, test results are to ISO 8655</li>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"541\" height=\"98\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Item</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Increment</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Test volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Inaccuracy</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Imprecision</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.01-2.5 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.05 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2.5 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.3 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1-5 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.3 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.2-10 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.2 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">10 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.3 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1-30 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.0 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">30 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.3 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1-50 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.0 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">50 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.3 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','DSR_Propenser_Dispenser_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(221,'Proline Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser','<p>Proline Prospenser is an easy-to-use Bottle-Top Dispenser. It has been  designed for trouble-free and reliable bottle-top dispensing of liquids,  including concentrated acids, bases, saline solutions, as well as many  organic solvents</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dispensing directly from the supply bottle</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Fully autoclavable at 121&#730;C , 2 bar, 20 minutes</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Accuracy of delivery within &plusmn;0.5% on maximum delivery</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;Chemically resistant liquid pathway</li>\r\n<li>Anti-drip closure cap included</li>\r\n<li>Easy to use volume adjustment for reproducibl dispensings</li>\r\n<li>Easy to dismantle for cleaning and maintenance</li>\r\n<li>Wide range of adapters are included to fit the most common bottle sizes</li>\r\n<li>Optional flexible dispense tube extention (max length 800 mm) with safety handle permits fast and precise dispensing even into narrow tubes</li>\r\n<li>Each unit is supplied with performance certificate and tested according to ISO 8655</li>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"575\" height=\"82\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Item</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Increment</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Test volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Inaccuracy</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Imprecision</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Proline Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.5&ndash;5 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.5 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Proline Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1-10 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.2 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.5 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Proline Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2.5-25 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.5 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.5 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Proline Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5-50 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.0 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.5 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','DSR_Proline_Prospenser_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(222,'Biotrate Digital Burette','<p>The streamlined Biotrate Digital Burette and dispenser delivers  accurate, precise and convenient bottle-top titration, as well as  optimum operator safety. Available in sizes 0-30 ml and 0-50 ml.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The head can be conveniently rotated 360&ordm; for operator safety and comfort. </li>\r\n<li> See-through barrel ensures bubble-free titration. </li>\r\n<li> Automatic switch-off without losing the previous titrated volume, when left unattended </li>\r\n<li> No dripping when in static mode </li>\r\n<li> A new safety pedestal valve allows the Biotrate liquid path to be turned off manually to prevent accidental delivery. Its right angled spout is also designed to enhance safety in use. </li>\r\n<li> Robust outer casing does not move during the priming or dispensing sequences. </li>\r\n<li> PTFE plunger and borosilicate glass barrel allow dispensing of aqueous solutions and some aggressive liquids. </li>\r\n<li> Powered by a 3.6V lithium battery giving a minimum life of 60,000 three-minute titrations. Automatic low battery voltage is indicated on the large easy-to-read LCD window. </li>\r\n<li> The liquid pathway is autoclavable</li>\r\n</ul>','<table class=\"specifications\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"565\" height=\"50\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<td>Item</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Channels</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Increment</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Test volume</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Inaccuracy</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Imprecision</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"grey_line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Biotrate Digital Burette</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0-30 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.01 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.2 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #999;\">\r\n<td>Biotrate Digital Burette</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0-50 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.01 ml</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.2 %</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0.1 %</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','DSR_Biotrate_Digital_Burette_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(223,'Biofiller','<p>Biofiller is a uniquely designed, lightweight and easy-to-use pipette filler with an ultra-squeezable bulb to provide smooth, manual pipetting control in both aspirating and dispensing, using 1 ml to 100 ml pipettes.<br /> <br /> Simply squeeze the large silicone bulb, and the thumb lever controls both the aspirating and dispensing modes, with a button to blow-out residual contents of pipette if required.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Comfortable and simple to use </li>\r\n<li>Precise pipetting control </li>\r\n<li>Robust and lightweight </li>\r\n<li>Large capacity bulb </li>\r\n<li>Compatible with blow-out pipettes </li>\r\n<li>Simple thumb button operation </li>\r\n<li>Uses integral 0.45 &micro;m, replaceable      membrane filter to ensure liquid is not accidentally drawn into the unit </li>\r\n<li>Autoclavable silicone pipette      holder </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','PAD_Biofiller_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(224,'Midi Plus Pipetting Controller','<p>Biohit Midi Plus is a lightweight cordless pipetting controller which allows aspiration from bottles and tubes without the arm and hand elevations required with serological or volumetric pipettes. It fits all commonly used glass or plastic pipettes, but can also be used with the Biohit 5 ml and 10 ml disposable tips. The speed can be fine-tuned by applying varying finger pressure to the operating buttons.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Precise finger tip control of      variable speed ranges </li>\r\n<li>Hydrophobic autoclavable filter      prevents from overaspiration </li>\r\n<li>Convenient fold-out bench stand      supports the unit and pipet when not in use* </li>\r\n<li>Linear speed control </li>\r\n<li>Low battery warning </li>\r\n<li>CE marked </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>','','PAD_Midi_Plus_Main_Image.jpg'),
	(225,'Other Accessories','<h1><strong>&nbsp;Other Accessories</strong></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>Wide range of accessories for Biohit pipettes and pipetting.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Proline Colour Coding Caps</strong></p>\r\n<p>Colour-code all your Proline mechanical pipettors with detachable caps. Six additional caps of different colour are available as accessories.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cat. number:</strong> 721234</p>\r\n<p><strong>Quantity:</strong> 6</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>Compatible for:</strong> Proline Mechanical Pipette</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Calibration tool/Tube opener </strong></p>\r\n<p>mLINE and Proline Plus can be easily calibrated using this elegant calibration tool. The tool also acts as a microtube opener.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cat. number:</strong> 726203</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>Compatible for:</strong> mLINE Mechanical Pipette, Proline Plus Mechanical Pipette</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Replacement filter, 0.45 &micro;m, autoclavable </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Cat. number:</strong> 712912</p>\r\n<p><strong>Quantity:</strong> 5</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>Compatible for:</strong> Midi Plus Pipetting Controller</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Replacement filter, 0.45 &micro;m, sterile</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Cat. number:</strong> 712913</p>\r\n<p><strong>Compatible for:</strong> Midi Plus Pipetting Controller</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;Midi Plus Adapter set for 5 ml tip</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Including the nose cone (PVDF) and the silicon adapter</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cat. number:</strong> 711015</p>\r\n<p><strong>Compatible for:</strong> Midi Plus Pipetting Controller</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;Midi Plus Adapter set for 10 ml tip</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Including the nose cone (PVDF) and the silicon adapter.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cat. 