	(37,'Weight Indicator Combics EX','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-005','PLS004','<ul>\r\n<li>Indicator for use in Zones 1,2 (explosive gasses) and Zones 20, 21, 22 (explosive dusts)</li>\r\n<li>For use with filling options \"Basic\" (H3) and \"Plus\" (H4) (automatically one-component filling).</li>\r\n<li>2 data interfaces as standard (1xRS232, 1x RS232, RS422, RS485 selectable by software)</li>\r\n<li>Verifiable class III,IIII</li>\r\n<li>Interface solutions for analogue output 4-20mA and Profibus DP</li>\r\n</ul>','EWI02','WI_COmbics_EX_Main_Image.jpg',140,1),
	(38,'Weighing Terminal CombicsPRO','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-004','BFS003','<ul>\r\n<li>High-contrast, backlit color graphics display, with 20mm display for weight readouts with status indicators, bargraph</li>\r\n<li>Stainless Steel Materia, IP67 protection rating.</li>\r\n<li>Connection of up to 2 analog weighing point and up to 62 Platforms/Scales connectable via xBPI-Protocol.</li>\r\n<li>Data Interface RS232, Ethernet and PS/2 as standard.</li>\r\n<li>Optional application program (e.g.batching, counting, manual recipe, filling, truck scale applications)</li>\r\n</ul>','WI03','WI_Combics_Pro_Main_Image.jpg',134,1),
	(39,'Midrics Indicator','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-004','BFS003','<p><strong>Midrics Scale Indicators MIS1</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Display: backlit, 14-segment, 20 mm LCD for weight readouts.</li>\r\n<li>Optional RS-232, RS-485, RS-422, 4-20mA</li>\r\n<li>Material: AISI 304 stainless steel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Midrics Scale Indicators MIS 2</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Display: backlit, 14-segment, 20 mm LCD for weight readouts, bar graph</li>\r\n<li>Connection for bar code scanner; battery operation</li>\r\n<li>Optional RS-232, RS-485, RS-422, 4-20mA, Digital I/O</li>\r\n<li>Applications: weighing, counting, checkweighing, classification (into three or five classes), totalizing, net-total, weighing in percent, neutral measurement.</li>\r\n<li>Material: AISI 304 stainless steel</li>\r\n</ul>','WI04','WI_Midrics_Main_Image.jpg',135,1),
	(40,'System Controller X4','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW001','<p>Multiple use device used in Industrial environment. Available multiple option card for flexible use and connection to peripheral devices and optional built-in application for process control.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SC01','PC_X4_Main_Image.jpg',141,1),
	(41,'System Controller X5','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW001','<p>The PRO-X5 System Controller is a multiple use device for precise weighing applications for industrial environment.. Available multiple option card for flexible use and connection to peripheral devices and optional built-in application for process control.</p>','SC02','SC_X5_Main_Image.jpg',142,1),
	(42,'System Controller X6','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW001','<p>The X6 System Controller family is designed as a micro-processor controlled weighing device with 19\" housing to be used in any kind of process automation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SC03','SC_X6_Main_Image.jpg',143,1),
	(43,'Analogue Process Transmitter PR1590, 1591 Series','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>Analogue process transmitter especially designed to be used in industrial environment and are particularly suited for applications with hazardous areas (zone 1) like chemical, petrochemical and food industries. The application ranges from simple transmitter device to control system used in conjunction with PLC.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>','PT01','PT_PR1590_Main_Image.jpg',144,1),
	(44,'Analogue Process Transmitter MP20','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','','PT02','PT_MP20_Main_Image.jpg',145,1),
	(45,'Digital Weighing Transmitter PR1710/11','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>Flexible weighing transmitter designed for use in industrial environment. Multiple output mode starting from analog connection to bus system provide connection to suit any modern industrial process . For hazardous area applications Sartorius provide an intrinsically safe version with load cell connection with W&amp;M approval for zone 1 and one application for zone 2 with W&amp;M approval as well.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','PT03','PT_PR1710_Main_Image.jpg',146,1),
	(46,'Digital Process Transmitter MP26','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>The MP 26 series of Digital Process Transmitters is designed to combine reliable weight information from process vessels with extremely easy operation and setup. A wide range of strain gauge load cells can be connected and output is provided in the common 4&hellip; 20 mA signal format. Front keys provide easy&nbsp; access to all configuration and operation levels. The MP 26/10 engineering tool provides the same level of access via a comfortable PC-Program.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','PT04','PT_MP26_Main_Image.jpg',147,1),
	(47,'Filedbus Transmitter PR1720','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>The PR 1720 Fieldbus Transmitter has features that guarantees; integral process automation to meet highest weighing requirements, analogue, digital and bus-capable signals for automation systems, connection of several load cells directly to the transmitter and the possibility to operate the instrument and to monitor the weighing process locally.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','PT05','PT_PR1720_Main_Image.jpg',148,1),
	(48,'Compact Filedbus Transmitter PR5210','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>The PR 5210 series of Digital Process Transmitters combine reliable and accurate weight acquisition with extremely easy operation and setup. The PR5210 is compact in design with easy access to all configuration and operation levels via the front serial interface.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','PT06','PT_PR5210_Main_Image.jpg',149,1),
	(49,'Ethernet Transmitter 24V DC PR 5220 ','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>The PR5220 is a compact DIN-Rail mounted transmitter that offers both reliability and ease of use for weighing recording via DMS weigh cells.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','PT07','PT_PR5220_Main_Image.jpg',150,1),
	(50,'Ethernet Transmitter PR5230 in Field Housing','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW002','<p>The PR5230 is the most flexible transmitter &nbsp;for readout and transmit weight values to installed networks and control systems. Multiple option cards are available to suit every industrial needs in terms of system connectivity. The robust stainless steel housing making it highly suitable for installation in industrial environment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','PT08','PT_PR5230_Main_Image.jpg',151,1),
	(51,'Process Indicator X3','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW003','<p>The new X3 Process Indicator provides an easy and reliable solution for process hopper scales with strain gauge load cells in process automation applications.</p>\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>','PI02','PI_X3_Main_Image.jpg',152,1),
	(52,'Precision Compression Load Cell PR6201','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW004','<p><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong></p>\r\n<p>500 kg &hellip; 300t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Accuracy (in % Emax)</strong></p>\r\n<p>for 500kg &hellip; 50: 0.25(LA/L), 0.04(D1), 0.015(C3).</p>\r\n<p>For 100t &hellip; 300t: 0.5 (LA/L), 0.06 (N/NE)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some Features</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hermetically sealed full stainless steel housing IP68 (Depth of 1.5m for 10,000 hrs), IP69K. Ex-version available(PR 6201/..E). High overload capacity. Resistant against vibrations. Optimum overvoltage protection.</p>','LC01','LC_PR6201_Main_Image.jpg',153,1),
	(53,'Compact Compression Load Cell PR6211','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW004','<p><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;30kg&hellip; 10t</p>\r\n<p><strong>Accucarcy (in %Emax)</strong></p>\r\n<p>For 30kg&hellip;3t : 0.05 (D1)</p>\r\n<p>For 500kg&hellip;5t : 0.25 (LT)</p>\r\n<p>For 500kg&hellip;10t : 0.04(D1)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some Features</strong></p>\r\n<p>Compact design. Hermetically sealed full stainless steel housing IP68 (Depth of 1.5m for 10,000 hrs). Ex-version available(500kg&hellip;10t). Resistant against vibrations. W&amp;M approval (acc. OIML R 60).</p>','LC02','LC_PR6211_Main_Image.jpg',154,1),
