	(78,'Twin-7 Stereoscopic Zoom Microscopes ','MEDLINE','CAT013','CMS004','<p>The&nbsp;Twin series&nbsp;of stereoscopic microscopes are&nbsp;designed for educational and professional&nbsp;use.&nbsp;They are&nbsp;particularly well suited to viewing specimens at low magnifications (with variable magnification) with the use of halogen illumination.</p>','SSM02','SSM_Twin7_Main_Image.jpg',90,1),
