	(175,'Process Controller X4 - TRUCK','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-003','TSC03','<p>Multiple use device used in Industrial environment. Available multiple  option card for flexible use and connection to peripheral devices and  optional built-in application for process control.</p>','TSI02','SC_X4_Main_Image.jpg',141,1),
	(176,'Process Controller X5 - TRUCK','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-003','TSC03','<p>The PRO-X5 System Controller is a multiple use device for precise  weighing applications for industrial environment.. Available multiple  option card for flexible use and connection to peripheral devices and  optional built-in application for process control.</p>','TSI03','SC_X5_Main_Image.jpg',142,1),
	(177,'Process Controller X6 - Truck','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-003','TSC03','<p>The X6 System Controller family is designed as a micro-processor  controlled weighing device with 19\" housing to be used in any kind of  process automation.</p>','TSI04','SC_X6_Main_Image.jpg',143,1),
	(178,'Wire Weights','SARTORIUS','CAT009','WGT001','<p>Individual E1 and E2 OIML class weights. The special steel wire weights  are available from 1 mg to 500 mg, are non-magnetisable and have a  density of 8.0 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. Packaged in a plastic case the wire weights are comfortably to store.</p>','WGT01','WGT_WIre_Weights_Main_Image.jpg',176,1),
	(179,'Knob Weights','SARTORIUS','CAT009','WGT001','<p>Individual E1, E2, F1, F2 and M1 OIML class weights. The special steel  knob weights are highly polished, corrosion-resistant and available from  1 g to 50 kg. They are non-magnetisable and have a density of 8.0 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. Packaged in a plastic case (up to 20 g) or a wooden case (from 50 g) the knob weights are comfortably to store.</p>','WGT02','WGT_Knob_Weights.jpg',177,1),
	(180,'Leaf Weights','SARTORIUS','CAT009','WGT001','<p>Individual F1 OIML class weights, made of aluminimum or nickel silver.  The aluminum leaf weights are available from 1 mg to 5 mg and have a  density of  2.7 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. The nickel silver leaf weights can be ordered from 10 mg to 500 mg and feature a density of  8.7 g/cm<sup>3</sup>. Packaged in a plastic case the leaf weights are comfortably to store.</p>','WGT03','WGT_Leaf_Weights_Main_Image.jpg',178,1),
	(181,'Block Shaped Weights','SARTORIUS','CAT009','WGT001','<p>ndividual block shaped M1 and M2 OIML class weights. The weights are  made of black painted grey cast . You can order the block shapped  weights from 5 kg to 50 kg.</p>','WGT04','WGT_Block_Shaped_Weights_Main_Image.jpg',179,1),
	(182,'Weight Sets','SARTORIUS','CAT009','WGT001','<p>Individual E1, E2, F1, F2 and M1 OIML class weight sets. The sets are  made of highly polished special steel, nickel silver, galvanised brass  or aluminium. Choose from weight sets including wire weights, leaf  weights or knob weights from 1 g to 50 kg.</p>','WGT05','WGT_Weights_Main_Image.jpg',180,1),
	(183,'Robot System Mass Comparator','SARTORIUS','CAT008','CMP001','<p>Robot systems for mass comparison of reference weights and test weights.  The fully automated mass comparator simplifies work in the mass  laboratory. This enables complete sets of mass standards and test  weights to be measured efficiently within the shortest time possible.  The weighing mode is entered on the PC, the number of comparison cycles  is defined and a direct 1:1 mass comparison or subdivision  (disseminationof mass for class E1 weights) is initiated by the robot  system.</p>','COM03','COM_Robot_System_Mass_Comparator_Main_Image.jpg',172,1),
	(184,'Vacuum Mass Comparator','SARTORIUS','CAT008','CMP001','<p>Sartorius has mastered the core disciplines of weighing like no other  company. Sartorius sets new standards in mass metrology. In cooperation  with the Bureau International des Poids et Mesures and the Institute for  Process Measurement and Sensor Technology of the Technical University  of Ilmenau, Sartorius has developed a mass comparator &mdash; the CCL1007 &mdash;  that is capable of determining differences in mass to an accuracy of 0.1  &mu;g for weights of 1 kg &mdash; even under high-vacuum conditions.</p>','COM04','COM_Vacuum_Mass_Comparator_Main_Image.jpg',171,1),
	(185,'Susceptometer','SARTORIUS','CAT008','CMP001','<p>Susceptometer for testing the magnetic properties of weights. Sartorius  susceptometer complete the range of accessories for high-resolution  balances and mass comparators. Along with its specialised software, the  susceptometer provides a unique, complete solution to ensure that the  limits of the weights\' magnetic properties are maintained.</p>','COM05','COM_Susceptometer_Main_Image.jpg',174,1),
	(186,'Volume and Density Determination','SARTORIUS','CAT008','CMP001','<p>Sartorius offers PC-controlled, user-friendly complete solutions for  determining the volume and density of E1 weights from 1 g to 1 kg.  Highly accurate volume comparators are equipped with sensors for air  density determination and for temperature measurement in a buoyancy  bath. The pycnometer delivers precise results in determining the volume  of E1 weights from 1 to 50 kg.<br />With these user-friendly solutions, Sartorius covers the entire range for determining the density of E1 weights.</p>','COM06','COM_Volume_and_Density_Determination_Main_Image.jpg',173,1),
	(187,'High Precision Climatestation for E1 lab YCM16C','SARTORIUS','CAT008','CMP001','<p>The Sartorius YCM16C climate station meets the highest accuracy  standards and is the perfect solution for determining air density. It is  used to monitor the room climate in all metrological laboratories.</p>','COM07','COM_High_Precision_Climatestation_Main_Image.jpg',175,1),
	(188,'Concrete Truck Scale Weighing Platform','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p><strong>Platfrom Size</strong></p>\r\n<p>Standard:&nbsp; 3x9m, 3x12m,3x15m,3x18m</p>\r\n<p>*Custom size available upon request</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Platform Capacity</strong></p>\r\n<p>Platform capacity depends on user requrement. Usual Capacity: 40,60,80 ton.</p>','TWP02','TWP_Concrete Truck Scale Weighing Platform.jpg',182,1),
	(189,'Software','SARTORIUS','CAT008','CMP001','<p>Careful acquisition of weighing data and associated parameters is one of  the most important criteria in mass metrology. Sartorius offers various  flexible software solutions for the administration and controlling of  comparators, climate stations, weights and other mass metrology  equipment.</p>','COM08','COM_Software.jpg',184,1),
	(190,'Truck Scale Load Cell PA6167','CN','CAT-IND-003','TSC001','<p><strong>Weighing Capacity </strong></p>\r\n<p>10,15,20,25,30,40,50t</p>\r\n<p><strong>Accuracy Class</strong></p>\r\n<p>0.03%</p>','TS03','TS_PA6167_Main_Image.jpg',1,1),
	(191,'Model A1 Truck Scale Weighing Platform','CHINA','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p>Model A1, Part No. 6711,middle dissected, with a top cover on the platform for access to the load cells</p>','TWP03','TWP_Model_A1_Main_Image.jpg',188,1),
	(192,'Model A2 Truck Scale Weighing Platform','CHINA','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p>Model A2, Part No. 6722, middle dissected, with side cover for access to load cells</p>','TWP04','Model A2.jpg',186,1),
	(193,'Model B1 Truck Scale Weighing Platform','CHINA','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p>Model B1, Part No. 6211, modularization type</p>','TWP05','TWP_Model_B1_Main_Image.jpg',187,1),
	(194,'Model B2 Truck Scale Weighing Platform','CHINA','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p>Model B2, Part No. 6222&nbsp;, modularization type</p>','TWP06','Model B2.jpg',189,1),
	(195,'Model B3 Truck Scale Weighing Platform','CHINA','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p>Model B3, Part No. 6233, modularization type, with gap in the middle</p>','TWP07','TWP_Model_B3_Main_Image.jpg',190,1),
	(196,'pH-Meter Electrodes','SARTORIUS','CAT002','PHM005','<p>pH-electrodes for pH-measurement systems. Choose between long lasting  fluid electrolytes with sophisticated measuring performance and  easy-to-operate gel electrodes. Intelligent electrodes save the  calibration data and thus assure full GLP compliance. pH-electrodes with  integrated temperature sensor are available.</p>','PHE001','PHE_Sartorius_pH_Electrode_Main_Image.jpg',191,1),
	(197,'Sartorius pH/Conductivity Meter Accessories','SARTORIUS','CAT002','PHM006','<p>pH-measurement accessories include probe arm assemblies for  pH-electrodes, GLP-compliant printers, printer ribbon cassettes and  printer paper. The pH-measurement accessories ease the handling with  pH-electrodes and improve the data documentation.</p>','PHA001','PHA_SArtorius_pH-Meter_Accessories.jpg',192,1),
	(198,'pH-Papers | Reagent Paper ','SARTORIUS','CAT002','PHM006','<p>pH-papers | reagent papers for accurate determination of the pH in water  samples and for measuring the pH of a sample during analysis, as well  as the determination of  the presence of a certain substance in a  sample. The pH-papers | reagent are available in rolls or strips and  allow for easy and fast pH determination with an accuracy sufficient for  nearly all routine pH-tests.</p>','PHA002','PHA_Reagent_Paper_Main_Image.jpg',193,1),
	(199,'Model C1 Truck Scale Weighing Platform','CHINA','CAT-IND-003','TCS003','<p>Model Cl , Part No. 6344, middle dissected, with a top cover on the platform for access to the load cells</p>\r\n<p>Model Cl , Part No. 6344, middle dissected, with a top cover on the platform for access to the load cells</p>','TWP08','yubocn.jpg',194,1),
	(200,'HPC Compression Load Cell','PT','CAT-IND-003','TSC001','<p>(30t &amp; 45t Stainless Steel IP68) Weighbridge.</p>','TS03','TLC_HPC Mini Pic.jpg',195,1),
	(201,'HPC IP67 Compression Load Cell','PT','CAT-IND-003','TSC001','<p>(30t &amp; 45t) Weighbridge, hopper, tank.</p>','TS04','TLC_HPC-IP67_Compression_Load_Cell_Main_Image_Mini.jpg',196,1),
	(202,'LMA200 Microwave Moisture Analyzer','SARTORIUS','CAT003','MOA002','<p>Moisture meter LMA200 for the moisture analysis in liquid and pasty  samples with a moisture content ranging from approx. 8 to 100 %. The  humidity meter uses microwave drying which produces results up to 300 x  faster than a drying oven for samples with high moisture content. A  built-in analytical weighing system inside the moisture meter LMA200  measures the weight loss of a sample and determines the end point at  which the sample has reached a constant weight.</p>','MMA01','MMA_LMA200_Main_Image.jpg',197,1),
	(203,'EC1XS Economy Ex-Complete Scale','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-005','BFS005','<p>Intrinsically safe industrial scale in stainless steel for weighing  ranges of 0.1 g up to 3 t with a resolution of 15,000d (intervals).  These industrial scales feature 11 different load plate dimensions, high  IP Protection and various options.</p>\r\n<p>Europe (ATEX): II 2 GD EEx ib IIB T4 T155&deg;C</p>','ECS01','ECS_Economy_Ex_Main_Image.jpg',198,1),
	(204,'EB -eries Economy Ex-Complete Scale','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-005','BFS005','<p>Affordable and reliable standard scales for use in hazardous areas. With  \"weighing\" function and one additional application program.Readability  0.2 up to 5 g. Weighing range 6 up to 150 kg.</p>','ECS02','ECS_Economy_Ex_EB-Series_Main_Image.jpg',199,1),
	(205,'ME36S Micro Balance','SARTORIUS','CAT001','BAL001','<p>This new <span class=\"results-highlight\">ME36S</span> microbalance features an exceptionally high weighing capacity of 31g and a readability of 1&micro;g. The <span class=\"results-highlight\">ME36S</span> is designed for weighing the smallest sample quantities even in  relatively heavy or bulky sample containers. The separate installation  of weighing unit and display and/or electronic unit not only reduces  thermal disturbances, but also delivers absolutely reliable weighing  results. By virtue of its unique design, the <span class=\"results-highlight\">ME36S</span> display and weighing units are close enough for ideal operating  convenience, with optimal spacing for ergonomic handling of microscopic  sample quantities.</p>','UM3','Microbalance_ME36S_Main_Image.jpg',200,1),
	(206,'Contego Weighing Module','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW004','<p><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong></p>\r\n<p>100kg to 2000 kg</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weighing Accuracy(in % Emax)</strong></p>\r\n<p>0.015 (C3), 0.04 (D1)<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some Features</strong></p>\r\n<p>It has been designed in strict compliance with the specification of the European Hygienic Engineering Design Group (EHEDG). The mounting plate is made of stainless steel grade 1.4404 and the protective cover is made of FDA-compliant sillicone to ensure reliable encapsulation of the module and prevents the intrusion of dirt and microorganisms.<br /> <br /></p>','LC10','LC_Contego_Weighing_Module_Main_Images.jpg',201,1),
	(207,'S-Type Load Cell MP76','SARTORIUS','CAT-IND-002','TSW004','<p><strong>Weighing Capacity</strong></p>\r\n<p>60kg...5t</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weighing Accuracy (in %Emax)</strong></p>\r\n<p>0.025 (C3), 0.03 (N)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some Features</strong></p>\r\n<p>Full stainless steel construction. High resolution and linearity. Hermetically welded seal (IP67). Robust and 100% maintenance free<br />.Approved according to OIML R60</p>','LC11','LC_MP76.jpg',202,1),
	(208,'mLINE Mechanical Pipettes','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS001','<p>mLINE<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span>is  Sartorius\'s most advanced mechanical pipette. It offers a unique  combination of novel and patented features for effortless accuracy and  precision. It is light weight, comfortable to use and<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span>is<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> frequently recommended by Health &amp; Safety Officers</span>. <br /><br />The  mLINE pipettes cover the full volume range of 0.1 &micro;l to 10 ml. These  fully autoclavable pipettes are available as single and multichannel  models.</p>','MPT01','MPT_mLINE_Mechanical_Pipette_Main_image.jpg',203,1),
	(209,'Proline Plus Mechanical Pipette','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS001','<p>The Proline Plus pipette family offers a wide variety of both fixed and  variable volume models as well as unique combination of novel and  patented features. High quality and light pipetting forces provide  pleasant pipetting experience. The Proline Plus with robust design is  suitable for variable every day laboratory applications. <br /><br />The Proline Plus pipettors cover the full range of 0.1&micro;l to 10ml.</p>','MPT02','MPT_Proline_Plus_Mechanical_Pipette_Main_Image.jpg',204,1),
	(210,'Proline Mechanical Pipette','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS001','<p>The original Sartrorius mechanical pipette from the Biohit <em>family</em> is designed for many different  types of routine laboratory work. Working with Proline, you will get  many years of reliable service. <br /><br />The Proline pipettes cover the  volume range 0.1 &micro;l to 5 ml with 8 different adjustable single-channel  and 8 adjustable multichannel models. Proline is also available in fixed  volume single-channel models.</p>','MPT03','MPT_Proline_Mechanical_Pipette_Main_Image.jpg',205,1),
	(211,'mLINE Starter Kit','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS001','<p>Sartorius mLINE Starter Kit of the Biohit <em>family&nbsp;</em>offers an opportunity to test and get started  with mLINE pipettes. You can choose between two Starter Kits with three  single-channel mLINE pipettes.</p>','MPT04','MPT_mLINE_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg',206,1),
	(212,'mLINE PCR Starter Kit','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS001','<p>mLINE PCR Starter Kit offers an easy start in PCR application. The fully autoclavable mLINE pipettes and sterile Sartorius SafetySpace<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&trade;</span> Filter Tips guarantee contamination free pipetting. The kits also incluce a cooling rack for microtubes, a cryo pen and other accessories.</p>','MPT05','MPT_mLINE_PCR_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg',207,1),
	(213,'Proline Plus Starter Kit','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS001','<p>Sartorius Proline&reg; Plus Starter Kit from the Biohit <em>family</em> offers an opportunity to test and get started with Proline Plus pipettes. You can choose between four Starter Kits with two or three single-channel Proline Plus pipettes.</p>','MPT06','MPT_Proline_Plus_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg',208,1),
	(214,'Picus Electronic Pipette','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS002','<p>Meet Picus &ndash; the Red Dot awarded electronic pipette that eases your work  load, protects you from injuries by ensuring optimal working posture  and allows accurate and precise pipetting results!<br /> <br /> Known as forerunner in liquid handling products with a long history in  developing ergonomic, high quality pipettes, Sartorius has now set a  completely new standard for electronic pipettes. A dedicated team of  R&amp;D and ergonomics professionals, together with laboratory  personnel, has developed a new technology with your needs and well being  in mind. The result is the most ergonomic and sophisticated pipette in  the market for laboratory professionals who demand the highest quality,  safety and reliability in their work.</p>','EPT01','EPT_Picus_Main_Image.jpg',209,1),
	(215,'eLINE Electronic Pipettes','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS002','<p>The electronic Sartorius eLINE pipette from the Biohit <em>family&nbsp;</em>is the market leader in performance  and ergonomics. This award winning (Pro Finnish Design 2001) pipette  takes the effort out of pipetting and significantly reduces the risk of  Repetitive Strain Injury (RSI).<br /> <br /> The comprehensive range of pipetting programs in eLINE reduces the need  for several work stages and enables you to dispense liquids twice as  fast compared to a mechanical pipette. The unique DC-motor concept with  build-in error control improves pipetting precision and allows more  reliable results.<br /> <br /> eLINE is available in single-channel models covering the volume range  of 0.1 to 5000 &mu;l and multichannel models from 0.2 to 1200 &mu;l.</p>','EPT02','EPT_eLINE_Electronic_Pipette_Main_Image.jpg',210,1),
	(216,'eLINE PCR Starter Kit','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS002','<p>The unique eLINE PCR Starter Kit speeds up the work and prevents pipetting errors in small volumes. The eLINE Lite Dispenser together with the Sterile Sartorius Dispenser Tips is accurate and fast tool in dispensing PCR Master Mix to 96 well plates</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>eLINE PCR Starter Kit offers:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pipettes for all standard pipetting volumes in PCR</li>\r\n<li>Contamination free and safe PCR processes</li>\r\n<li>Accurate and precise results</li>\r\n<li>Twice faster MasterMix dispensing by using eLINE Lite Dispenser compared to manual pipetting</li>\r\n<li>User-independent result </li>\r\n</ul>','EPT03','EPT_eLINE_Starter_Kit_Main_Image.jpg',211,1),
	(217,'Optifit Pipette Tips','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS003','<p>In liquid handling, the pipette and the tip always form a system.  Perfect tip fitting and sealing to the pipette secures the best possible  accuracy and precision. Thus Biohit\'s precision-made Optifit Pipette  Tips, filtered and non-filtered, are made to provide excellent  reproducibility and accuracy. They fit perfectly with Biohit pipettes  and are suitable for use with most other pipette brands.</p>','PPT01','PPT_Optifit_Pipette_Tip_Main_Image.jpg',212,1),
	(218,'SafetySpace Filter Top','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS003','<p>Sartorius Biohit&rsquo;s SafetySpace Filter Tips are made of virgin polypropylene and  they feature filter (PE) barriers to prevent aerosol and liquid  contamination. This helps protect against the risk of  cross-contamination and reduces maintenance requirements of the  pipette.&nbsp; <br /><br />The filter tips are well suited for molecular biology, microbiology, cell culture ad radioactive work. <br /><br />SafetySpace  Filter Tips have more space between the sample and the filter than  conventional filter tips. With SafetySpace Filter Tips you do not need  to worry about the sample touching the filter whatever pipetting  technique or type of liquid you&rsquo;re using.</p>','PPT02','PPT_Safety_Space_Main_Image.jpg',1,1),
	(219,'Filter Tip, Regular','SARTORIUS','CAT014','LHS003','<p>Filter tips with regular air gap are made of polypropylene. Filter tips are tray-packed, electron beam pre-sterilized and certified as RNase, DNase and endotoxin free.</p>','PPT03','PPT_Filter_Tip_Regular_Main_Image.jpg',214,1),
	(220,'eLINE Lite Dispenser','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>The automated liquid handling operation offers accurate and repetitive  dispensing also with viscous, infectuous and high vapour pressure  liquids. <br /><br />The unique TipGuide selects and displays the most  suitable tip size which saves time and eliminates the possibility of an  incorrect tip selection.</p>','DSR01','DSR_eLINE_Lite_Dispenser_Main_Image.jpg',215,1),
	(221,'eLINE Pro DIspenser','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>eLINE Pro Dispenser offers&nbsp;you the most convenient and ergonomic  approach to multiple dispensing. Automated operations&nbsp;guarentees  accurate and repetitive dispensing also with viscous, infectuous and  high vapour pressure liquids.</p>','DSR02','DSR_eLINE_Pro_Dispenser_Main_image.jpg',216,1),
	(222,'Biohit Mechanical Stepper','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>The Biohit Mechanical Stepper is an easy-to-use positive displacement  instrument which allows rapid multi-dispensing of pre-set volumes up to  48 times in succession without refilling.</p>\r\n<p>The unit comes complete with an adapter for 25 ml and 50 ml syringes.</p>\r\n<p>The Biohit Mechanical Stepper is compatible with various syringe brands.</p>','DSR03','DSR_Mechanical_Stepper_Main_Image.jpg',217,1),
	(223,'Biohit Dispenser Tips','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>The Dispenser Tip functions according to positive displacement  principle, which allows for contamination-free dispensing and accurate  results also with high vapour, viscous and foaming liquids.</p>\r\n<p>Biohit Dispenser Tips are compatible with both eLINE dispenser and the Mechanical Stepper.</p>\r\n<p>The tip is made of virgin polypropylene (tip) and polyethylene (plunger). They are DNase, RNase, ATP and Pyrogen free.</p>','DSR04','DSR_Biohit_Dispenser_Tips_Main_Image.jpg',218,1),
	(224,'Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>The easy-to-use Prospensers deliver trouble-free and reliable dispensing of liquids including strong acids, bases and solvents.<br /><br />All  models are fitted with an anti-drip safety valve, a feature which  guards against drips when the Prospenser is not in use. A fine  adjustment mechanism allows even greater reproducibility for repeat  dispensing. The Prospenser features easy-to-adjust calibration  mechanism.<br /><br />Unlike other bottle-top dispensers, Prospenser&rsquo;s glass  barrel can be disassembled from the pedestal for thorough cleaning.  This also ensures that in the unlikely event of damage the glass barrel  can be replaced as a spare part.</p>','DSR05','DSR_Propenser_Dispenser_Main_Image.jpg',219,1),
	(225,'Proline Prospenser Bottle-Top Dispenser ','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>Proline Prospenser is an easy-to-use Bottle-Top Dispenser. It has been  designed for trouble-free and reliable bottle-top dispensing of liquids,  including concentrated acids, bases, saline solutions, as well as many  organic solvents.</p>','DSR06','DSR_Proline_Prospenser_Main_Image.jpg',221,1),
	(226,'Biotrate Digital Burette','Biohit','CAT014','LHS004','<p>The streamlined Biotrate Digital Burette and dispenser delivers  accurate, precise and convenient bottle-top titration, as well as  optimum operator safety. Available in sizes 0-30 ml and 0-50 ml.</p>','DSR07','DSR_Biotrate_Digital_Burette_Main_Image.jpg',222,1),
	(227,'Biofiller','Biohit','CAT014','LHS006','<p>Biofiller is a uniquely designed, lightweight and easy-to-use pipette  filler with an ultra-squeezable bulb to provide smooth, manual pipetting  control in both aspirating and dispensing, using 1 ml to 100 ml  pipettes.<br /><br />Simply squeese the large silicone bulb, and the thumb  lever controls both the aspirating and dispensing modes, with a button  to blow-out residual contents of pipette if required.</p>','PAD01','PAD_Biofiller_Main_Image.jpg',223,1),
	(228,'Midi Plus Pipetting Controller','Biohit','CAT014','LHS006','<p>Biohit Midi Plus is a lightweight cordless pipetting controller which allows aspiration from bottles and tubes without the arm and hand elevations required with serological or volumetric pipettes. It fits all commonly used glass or plastic pipettes, but can also be used with the Biohit 5 ml and 10 ml disposable tips.</p>\r\n<p>The speed can be fine-tuned by applying varying finger pressure to the operating buttons.</p>','PAD02','PAD_Midi_Plus_Main_Image.jpg',224,1),
	(229,'Refill Tip Box','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p>Empty Tip Boxes for refill system.</p>','PAC01','PAC_Refill_Tip_Box_Main_Image.jpg',228,1),
	(230,'Safe Cone Filters','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p>These unique and replaceable polyethylene (PE) filters act as a final  barrier to prevent any fluids and liquid vapours from reaching the  internal components of the pipette.</p>','PAC02','PAC_Safe_Cone_Filters_Main_Image.jpg',229,1),
	(231,'Pipette Stands','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p>When the pipette is not in use, it should be stored in an upright position in order to avoid contamination<br />from dirty benches. Biohit offers stands for all of its pipettes.</p>','PAC03','PAC_Pipette_Stands_Main_Image.jpg',1,0),
	(232,'Decontamination','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Biohit Proline Biocontrol</strong> is ready for use decontamination solution for laboratory equipment such  as pipettes, centrifuges, CO2 incubators, and surfaces.</p>','PAC04','PAC_Decontamination_Main_Image.jpg',231,1),
	(233,'Elbow Pad','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p>Pipetting is sometimes heavy work. Hand and shoulders get tired easily  in long pipetting series.Improve your working posture with Biohit Elbow  Pad. The Elbow Pad is a solution to a more relaxed and ergonomic work.  The visco elastic material of the pad relieves contact stress, pain and  discomfort during pipetting.</p>','PAC05','PAC_Elbow_Pad_Main_Image.jpg',232,1),
	(234,'Ergomate','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p>Biohit  Ergomate removes the need to hold the plate at any angle and  allows safe dispensing, resulting easier, safer and more precise  pipetting.</p>','PAC06','PAC_Ergomate.jpg',233,1),
	(235,'Reagent Vessel','Biohit','CAT014','LHS005','<p>Biohit Reagent Vessels for use especially with all multichannel  pipettes. Chemically resistant Vessels are made of polypropylene for  cost-effective reuse and  autoclavability.</p>','PAC07','PAC_Reagent_Vessel_Main_Image.jpg',234,1),
